title: Bug 121682: Exception thrown when exporting data from table containing highlight/map
description: Exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.
OB: When exporting data from a table that contains a group row with a highlight rule and a map rule, an exception is thrown.
EB: No exception should be thrown when exporting data from a table that contains a group row with a highlight rule and a map rule.
SR:
Steps to reproduce:
1. Create a table with a group row that includes a highlight rule and a map rule.
2. Preview the attached report.
3. Attempt to export the data from the table.
